I'll make this one fairly basic, so you can have a slow start :)
Okay, there will be two basic Werewolves against a Seer, Protector and 2 Vanilla Villagers.
To access your power at night, you click on the little people icon (that currently has a 6 next to it) and choose your target
During the day, you press the same button to vote.
If you forget what your role does, hit the icon with the "i"
If you're not sure what role you are, there will be a small button with an (i) in it, click on that to find out.
It will tell you what to do
Wolves can talk to each other at night, but you cannot talk secretly during the day.
